IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EVAL-TEST.

DATA DIVISION.
01 X PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 Y PICTURE IS 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 15 TO X
    MOVE 25 TO Y

    EVALUATE X
        WHEN 10 THROUGH 20
            DISPLAY "X IN 10-20 RANGE"
        WHEN OTHER
            DISPLAY "X NOT IN 10-20"
    END

    EVALUATE X ALSO Y
        WHEN 15 ALSO 25
            DISPLAY "BOTH MATCH"
        WHEN OTHER
            DISPLAY "OTHER MATCH"
    END

    EVALUATE TRUE
        WHEN X > 10
            DISPLAY "X IS GREATER THAN 10"
        WHEN OTHER
            DISPLAY "X IS NOT"
    END.
